<paragraph blockId="5.[264,1323,353,1902]" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[264,436,353,379]" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Body (male):</emphasis>
Length: 
<quantity box="[562,716,353,379]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.75" metricValueMax="5.2" metricValueMin="4.3" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" unit="mm" value="4.75" valueMax="5.2" valueMin="4.3">4.3–5.2 mm</quantity>
; pronotal width: 
<quantity box="[945,1128,353,379]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.7" metricValueMax="10.3" metricValueMin="9.1" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" unit="mm" value="0.97" valueMax="1.03" valueMin="0.91">0.91–1.03 mm</quantity>
; crown length: 
<quantity box="[264,444,393,419]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.65" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="2.3" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" unit="mm" value="0.265" valueMax="0.3" valueMin="0.23">0.23–0.30 mm</quantity>
; crown production: 
<quantity box="[697,877,393,419]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.15" metricValueMax="1.3" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" unit="mm" value="0.115" valueMax="0.13" valueMin="0.1">0.10–0.13 mm</quantity>
; crown production ratio: 
<number box="[1197,1318,393,419]" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" value="0.44" valueMax="0.52" valueMin="0.36">0.36–0.52</number>
; interocular width: 
<quantity box="[500,684,433,459]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.05" metricValueMax="5.5" metricValueMin="4.6" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" unit="mm" value="0.505" valueMax="0.55" valueMin="0.46">0.46–0.55 mm</quantity>
; face length: 
<quantity box="[871,1055,433,459]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.08" metricValueMax="1.13" metricValueMin="1.03" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" unit="mm" value="1.08" valueMax="1.13" valueMin="1.03">1.03–1.13 mm</quantity>
; interantennal width: 
<quantity box="[264,445,473,499]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.45" metricValueMax="4.9" metricValueMin="4.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" unit="mm" value="0.445" valueMax="0.49" valueMin="0.4">0.40–0.49 mm</quantity>
. Dried specimens yellow­green to gold, with no distinctive markings, scutellum of some with yellow or cream markings. Forewings subhyaline in basal twothirds, hyaline apically; third apical cell stalked (
<number box="[867,882,556,582]" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" value="3.0">3</number>
rd and 
<number box="[960,975,556,582]" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" value="4.0">4</number>
th apical veins fused basally) arising from cell R. 
<collectingCountry box="[504,563,596,622]" name="India" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Hind</collectingCountry>
wings characteristic for genus. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[941,1126,596,622]" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Body (female):</emphasis>
Length: 
<quantity metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.65" metricValueMax="4.8" metricValueMin="4.5" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" unit="mm" value="4.65" valueMax="4.8" valueMin="4.5">4.5–4.8 mm</quantity>
; pronotal width: 
<quantity box="[528,707,636,662]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" metricValueMax="1.06" metricValueMin="0.94" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" unit="mm" value="1.0" valueMax="1.06" valueMin="0.94">0.94–1.06 mm</quantity>
; crown length: 
<quantity box="[905,1084,636,662]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.75" metricValueMax="2.9" metricValueMin="2.6" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" unit="mm" value="0.275" valueMax="0.29" valueMin="0.26">0.26–0.29 mm</quantity>
; crown production: 
<quantity box="[264,444,676,702]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.15" metricValueMax="1.3" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" unit="mm" value="0.115" valueMax="0.13" valueMin="0.1">0.10–0.13 mm</quantity>
; crown production ratio: 
<number box="[766,887,676,702]" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" value="0.41000000000000003" valueMax="0.46" valueMin="0.36">0.36–0.46</number>
. Color, markings, and wings as in males.
</paragraph>
